gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Mavericks 112, Wizards 104
gameRecap.excerpt: The Mavericks have now won five consecutive games as they defeat the Wizards, 112-104. Luka Doncic led the Mavericks with 26 points, 15 assists, and 11 rebounds as Kyrie Irving (26 points, seven rebounds, four assists) and Daniel Gafford (16 points, career-high tying 17 rebounds) totaled 42 points. Deni Avdiji led Washington with 25 points and seven rebounds as Tyus Jones added 14 points and a career-high 16 assists. Dallas moves to 31-23 as Washington moves to 9-44.
